                <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Fore self reference:</p>
<p>To restore default branch from a tag while preserving history, do:</p>
<p>{% highlight shell %}
$ git checkout tags/v1.2.3 -b v1.2.3
$ git diff main &gt; /tmp/diff.patch
$ git checkout main
$ cat /tmp/diff.patch | git apply
$ git commit -am &ldquo;Rolled back to v1.2.3&rdquo;
$ git push origin main
{% endhighlight %}</p>
]]></content>
            

